              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <button onClick={() => setIsAIOpen(true)} className="bg-[#1b2e22] text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full text-[9px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase shadow-xl hover:bg-[#2d6a4f] transition-all active:scale-95">
          ✦ AI Advisor
